Title : Shamkir Chess
Text : [[File:Shamkir Chess tournament (1) .jpg|thumb|right|upright=1.5|Shamkir Chess 2014, playing hall]]
'''Shamkir Chess''' is a [[chess]] supertournament played in [[Şəmkir|Shamkir]], [[Azerbaijan]] in memory of [[Vugar Gashimov]] (1986–2014).<ref>{{cite web|title=Vugar Gashimov Memorial – Press Release|url=http://www.chessdom.com/vugar-gashimov-memorial-press-release/|work=www.chessdom.com|accessdate=24 April 2014}}</ref>

